items.summary: Remove the onboarding step that asks the user to choose between romantic vs friendship (the “Looking for?” step) from the multi-step profile setup dialog, so new users are no longer prompted with that question during onboarding.

Ensure profile creation still sends valid backend-required fields even after removing the romantic vs friendship onboarding step by applying a safe default relationship intent value for newly created profiles.
Update the Profile page UI so the removed romantic vs friendship question is not shown as a profile field (neither in view mode nor edit mode), while keeping profile updates functional.
